What is Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt?
Lean Six Sigma Yellow Belt is an introductory certification that provides employees with the 
foundational tools and mindset to identify inefficiencies, solve problems using data, and improve 
everyday processes. It equips you with practical skills to streamline work, reduce waste, and 
contribute to higher‑quality outcomes across our organization.
Why join the training program?
By joining the Yellow Belt program, you’ll:
• Gain practical problem-solving.
• Support process improvement projects and contribute to team initiatives.
• Strengthen your analytical capabilities for better decision-making.
• Ideal for service delivery managers, business analysts, and process improvement 
specialists focused on continuous improvement.
• Enhance your skills and help foster HP Solutions’ culture of ongoing improvement.
